Page Header Specification

Structure
- Full-width header with two rows.
- Top row: logo placeholder + app name on left, mode toggle on right.
- Bottom row: breadcrumb navigation.

Components
- Use shadcn/ui only.
- Logo placeholder: 32x32 square, rounded, muted background, border.
- App name text: "BasisScope", semibold, larger text size.
- Mode toggle: existing `ModeToggle` component.
- Breadcrumb: shadcn `Breadcrumb` with placeholder items.

Layout
- Header padding: 24px horizontal, 16px vertical.
- Header background uses `bg-background`.
- Header bottom border uses `border-b border-border`.
- Breadcrumb row has top padding for separation.